name: LEGO Star Wars: The Skywalker Saga Prototype
name_original: LEGO Star Wars: The Skywalker Saga Prototype
description:
LEGO Star Wars: The Skywalker Saga Prototype is an action-fighting game developed by EvanColeGaming. It came out on 07-07-2021.
You can play LEGO Star Wars: The Skywalker Saga Prototype on PC. The game is sold via itch.io.
